com.olliebown.beads.data
Class SampleManager

java.lang.Object
  com.olliebown.beads.data.SampleManager

public class SampleManager
extends java.lang.Object

SampleManager keeps a central store for samples that are being loaded into memory and can be used to organise samples into groups.
